queries.sql: SELECT `visa_request`.*, `branches`.`name` as `branch_name`, `client`.`org_name` as `client_name`, `client`.`branch` as `branch`, `client`.`agency` as `agency`, `client`.`email` as `client_email`, `client`.`mobile_no` as `client_mobile`, `country`.`country` as `country_name`, `category`.`category` as `visa_type_name`, `status`.`status_value` FROM `visa_request` JOIN `client` ON `visa_request`.`client_id` = `client`.`client_id` JOIN `branches` ON `visa_request`.`branch_id` = `branches`.`branch_id` JOIN `country` ON `visa_request`.`country_of_visit` = `country`.`id` JOIN `category` ON `visa_request`.`visa_type` = `category`.`id` JOIN `status` ON `visa_request`.`status` = `status`.`status_id` WHERE `visa_request`.`client_id` = '4' AND `visa_request`.`is_active` = 1 AND `visa_request`.`visa_request_id` = '3' ORDER BY `visa_request`.`visa_request_id` DESC
